RISE ASCII SCENE 5
#############################################################################################################
#                                      RISE Ascii Scene File                                                #
#                                                                                                           #
#   File:           optimal_mis_test_baseline.RISEscene                                                     #
#   Description:    Baseline version of optimal_mis_test.RISEscene with power heuristic only.               #
#   Author:         Aravind Krishnaswamy                                                                    #
#   Birthdate:      April 9, 2026                                                                           #
